OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Sign Language set  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor legal recognition      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Sign Language (BSL) will gain  
OL,6, formal recognition under legislation   
OL,7, set to be passed by MPs.               
OL,9,FThe bill, which sailed through its     
OL,10,Ffirst hurdle in the Commons in January,
OL,11,Fwould require public bodies to promote 
OL,12,Fthe language.                          
OL,14,FIt will also recognise BSL as a        
OL,15,Flanguage in its own right in England,  
OL,16,FWales and Scotland.                    
OL,18,FThe final scrutiny stage in the Commons
OL,19,Fwill take place later, after which the 
OL,20,Fbill will go to the House of Lords.    
